staying power within the organization. Often this person is the one who
benefits most from your work or someone who felt the most pain before you came
along.</p>

<p>Never never never never burn bridges.</p>

<p>If you specialize, specialize in a type of customer rather than a technology.</p>

<p>Referrals are #1 source of leads for basically every freelancer, followed by
