<h3 id="double-your-freelancing-rate-2">Double Your Freelancing Rate <a href="https://doubleyourfreelancing.com/">2</a></h3>

<p>Strive to understand the pain that the customer is feeling.</p>

<p>Always qualify the value that you bring to the table.</p>

<p>In doing so we show that:</p>

<ol>
