doing this get us closer to the solution?‚Äù If a particular requirement didn‚Äôt
get us any closer, and the cost of that requirement wasn‚Äôt outweighed by its
ultimate ROI, it was shelved or reformulated to achieve those two ends.‚Äù</p>

<p>‚ÄúPlanning a roadmap should never be done in isolation. It shouldn‚Äôt be
