get to the goal as quickly, cheaply, and reliably as possible?‚Äù</p>

<p>A solution is the inverse of a problem.</p>

<p>There are many paths, or roadmaps, that connect a problem with a solution.</p>

<p>Roadmaps get to a solution with varying degrees of sophistication and completeness.</p>

<p>A roadmap should be planned by both the driver (you) and the navigator (the client.)</p>

<p>How we justify our rates:
‚ÄúThe reason we are hired is to satisfy our clients. This doesn‚Äôt mean just
having a good relationship with them; it means helping make their business
